{
  "total_duration": 685.453,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 15.152,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你有没有遇到过这种事：今晚的电影票、演出票、活动名额已经"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，页面上没有票了。突然有人退了两张，你赶紧点进去，结果发现日期不是今晚，是下周三。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 15.502,
      "end": 36.053,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“票已售完”。这不是单纯的“没买到票”，而是一次买票过程里的三次转折："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、有人"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return tickets"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、最后发现是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "next Wednesday's performance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 36.403,
      "end": 54.211,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把旧场景接到现在。现在买电影票、演唱会票，常常是在 App 里选日期、选场次、选座位。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是剧院门口的实体售票窗口，有人站在窗口后面卖票、退票。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 54.561,
      "end": 73.148,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还要分清"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "performance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一部戏；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "performance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是这部戏的一场演出。同一部"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以今晚演一场，也可以下周三再演一场。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 73.498,
      "end": 88.914,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课的笑点是：票是真的，机会也像是真的，可是它救不了今晚这一场。今天要抓住这条链："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "late for play, sold out, returned tickets, sudden hope, wrong performance, sad choice"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 89.264,
      "end": 98.399,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，主人公和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Susan"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "匆匆赶向剧院。他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The play may begin at any moment."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 98.749,
      "end": 111.933,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "at any moment"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是随时、马上就可能发生。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may begin"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是请求，而是猜测：这场戏可能马上开始。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 112.283,
      "end": 123.091,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Susan"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更担心，她回答："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It may have begun already."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话是在猜一个更早的可能：也许它已经开始了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 123.44,
      "end": 131.128,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，主人公赶到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这是一个实体售票窗口，不是手机 App。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 131.478,
      "end": 143.214,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他很礼貌地问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I have two tickets please?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I have"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是礼貌请求，意思是“请卖给我两张票，可以吗？”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 143.564,
      "end": 159.375,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但窗口后的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "girl"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm sorry, we've sold out."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是所有票都卖完了，一张也不剩。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Susan"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "只好说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "What a pity!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 159.725,
      "end": 170.481,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，事情突然转向。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Just then, a man hurried to the ticket office."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正在这时，一个人也匆匆跑到售票窗口。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 170.831,
      "end": 185.926,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Can I return these two tickets?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“回来”，而是把票退回去，可能是退票、退款，或者至少把这两张票交还给售票处。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 186.276,
      "end": 198.016,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公一听到有两张票被退回来，马上看到了希望。他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "went back to the ticket office at once"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，然后问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Could I have those two tickets please?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 198.366,
      "end": 208.058,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，希望又被戳破了。那位"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "girl"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Certainly, but they're for next Wednesday's performance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 208.407,
      "end": 218.999,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话非常关键。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "performance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一场演出，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "next Wednesday's performance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是下周三那一场，不是今晚这一场。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 219.349,
      "end": 230.389,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这不是开心结尾。他得到的是两张真票，但不是他和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Susan"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "赶来看的一场。最后他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I might as well have them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 230.739,
      "end": 242.346,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "might as well"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里不是兴奋地“太好了”，而是有点无奈：虽然不是我想要的，但也只好这样了。所以课文最后加了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sadly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 242.696,
      "end": 260.272,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文最容易误会三个地方。第一，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么？第二，有人"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return tickets"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么不等于问题解决？第三，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I might as well have them"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到底是什么心情？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 260.622,
      "end": 264.28,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 App 吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 264.63,
      "end": 276.986,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。在这篇故事里，它是剧院门口的实体售票窗口。你可以想象成以前没有手机选座时，人们直接到窗口问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I have two tickets please?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 277.336,
      "end": 281.303,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么意思？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 281.653,
      "end": 299.273,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是票或者商品已经全部卖完。电影票、演唱会票、限量玩具、热门课程名额，都可以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sell out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文里是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "we've sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是今晚这场没有票了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 299.623,
      "end": 302.268,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是后来不是有人退票了吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 302.618,
      "end": 317.281,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，这是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "false rescue"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，看起来救了他，其实没有。那个人问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Can I return these two tickets?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是退回票，不是人回来了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 317.631,
      "end": 320.268,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "退回来的票为什么不能用？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 320.617,
      "end": 334.893,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它们是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "for next Wednesday's performance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。同一部"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "有很多场"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "performances"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他要看的是今晚这一场，票却是下周三那一场。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 335.243,
      "end": 340.478,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I might as well have them"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是开心吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 340.828,
      "end": 354.48,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是开心，是有点认命。像你本来想买今晚的票，结果只能买下周三的票，你可能会说：算了，也只能这样了。这就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I might as well have them"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的味道。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 354.83,
      "end": 358.046,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"The play may begin at any moment,\" I said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 358.396,
      "end": 361.78,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"It may have begun already,\" Susan answered."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 362.13,
      "end": 364.722,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I hurried to the ticket office."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 365.072,
      "end": 369.272,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"May I have two tickets please?\" I asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 369.621,
      "end": 373.005,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"I'm sorry, we've sold out,\" the girl said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 373.355,
      "end": 377.195,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"What a pity!\" Susan exclaimed."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 377.545,
      "end": 381.001,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Just then, a man hurried to the ticket office."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 381.351,
      "end": 384.639,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"Can I return these two tickets?\" he asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 384.989,
      "end": 387.581,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"Certainly,\" the girl said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 387.931,
      "end": 391.075,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I went back to the ticket office at once."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 391.425,
      "end": 395.793,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"Could I have those two tickets please?\" I asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 396.143,
      "end": 402.791,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"Certainly,\" the girl said, \"but they're for next Wednesday's performance. Do you still want them?\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 403.14,
      "end": 406.38,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"I might as well have them,\" I said sadly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 406.73,
      "end": 409.274,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
