        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 409.624,
      "end": 411.16,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "ticket"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 411.51,
      "end": 422.614,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "ticket"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是票，表示你可以进入某个地方或参加某个活动。以前可能是一张纸票，现在也可能是手机里的二维码票。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 422.964,
      "end": 437.787,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "ticket"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "电影票可以说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a movie ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，火车票是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a train ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，演出票是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a theatre ticket"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文里主人公问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I have two tickets please?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 438.137,
      "end": 440.889,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "return"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 441.239,
      "end": 442.919,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "return"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 443.269,
      "end": 460.136,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "return"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "常见意思是回来，但在这课里，它的意思是退回、归还。你可以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return a book"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把书还回图书馆；也可以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return a product"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把商品退回商店。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 460.486,
      "end": 471.15,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "return"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里那个人问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Can I return these two tickets?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "意思是“我可以退掉这两张票吗？”这两张票被退回来了，但日期不对。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 471.5,
      "end": 474.18,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pity"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pity"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 474.53,
      "end": 476.066,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pity"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pity"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 476.416,
      "end": 486.479,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pity"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pity"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里表示令人失望、可惜的事。计划失败了，票卖完了，你可以说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "What a pity!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 486.829,
      "end": 498.429,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pity"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Susan"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "说这句话的时候，不是大哭，也不是生气，而是很失望：他们已经赶到剧院了，可是票已经"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 498.779,
      "end": 512.499,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grammar"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是背一整张情态动词表，而是看"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "could"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "might"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在买票现场分别完成什么任务。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 512.848,
      "end": 529.656,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一组是猜测："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The play may begin at any moment."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may begin"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示“可能马上开始”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It may have begun already."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may have begun"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示“可能已经开始了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 530.006,
      "end": 547.225,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组是礼貌请求："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I have two tickets please?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Could I have those two tickets please?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "都是在请对方把票卖给我。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Could I have"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比直接说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Can I have"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更软一点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 547.575,
      "end": 559.338,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三组是无奈选择："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I might as well have them."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "might as well"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是：不是最理想，但既然这样，我也只好要了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 559.688,
      "end": 575.48,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样记：故事开头的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是担心和猜测；售票窗口的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Could I"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是礼貌买票；结尾的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "might as well"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是失望后的接受。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 575.83,
      "end": 584.981,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "语法跟着情绪走："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "worry, polite asking, sudden hope, wrong date, sad acceptance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这比单独背规则更容易记住。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 585.331,
      "end": 607.075,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out story"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "放进你自己的生活。想象你要买电影票、演唱会票、展览票，或者预约一个活动名额。你看到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，然后有人"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "returned two tickets"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，你很快去抢，却发现日期或场次不对。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 607.425,
      "end": 622.361,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以用这个小框架："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The tickets were sold out. Then someone returned two tickets. I hurried to buy them, but they were for next Wednesday's performance. I might as well wait or choose another day."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 622.71,
      "end": 632.926,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下面练习里，用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "word bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "填三个空，把“票卖完了、有人退票、结果场次不对”说清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 633.276,
      "end": 656.72,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：听课文全文 -> 听原音 -> 录一句 -> 获取反馈，把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The play may begin at any moment"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "we've sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return these two tickets"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "next Wednesday's performance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I might as well have them"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "读出清楚的转折。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 657.07,
      "end": 685.453,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "跟读之后，再做 ① 生活场景，用英语说一个买票或预约时发现日期、场次不对的小故事；后面 ② 完形 ③ 中译英 ④ 英译中 ⑤ 默写 一条线做下来。做完以后，爸爸的邮箱里就会收到你今天的成绩。记住，今天真正的笑点不是拿到票，而是拿到的票救不了今晚这一场："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wrong performance, sad choice"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    }
